## Description

This frontend of the "Find My Recipes" application â€” a responsive web interface for discovering recipes based on ingredients you already have at home. This user-friendly application helps users find recipes with food they already have, this is designed to be a qucik and easy use tool to make home cooked meals without having to go to the store.

